data.description: Showings begin Friday 2/16 - Any offers received will be reviewed by the seller on Monday 2/19.  Welcome to your charming retreat in the heart of Livonia! This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom bungalow offers both comfort and convenience. Nestled on a corner lot, this home boasts not only a prime location but also the highly sought-after Livonia Schools district.  Step inside to discover a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living areas are filled with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance throughout.  Outside, you'll find a private oasis waiting to be enjoyed. The expansive yard offers plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening, while the Clements Circle pool and park just steps away provide endless opportunities for recreation and leisure.  With its desirable location, well maintained condition, and access to top-notch amenities, this Livonia gem is truly a rare find. Don't miss your chance to make it yours – schedule your showing today!
